          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has a huge estate on 235 acres in the Atlanta, Georgia area he calls The Promised Land. Considering the man reportedly owns over 100 cars, we might agree with the nomenclature. The newest addition to Ross’ collection is a classic fire truck, something people are finding odd.",
